CustomField.description: This field will be used for Expere Doc Prep, which has not yet been implemented. This field is not required. It is manually populated. It specifies the interest rate of the deposit account. If an initial rate (such as a teaser) applies, this is the rate that is in effect after the expiration of the teaser period.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The interest rate of the deposit account. If an initial rate (i.e. a teaser) applies this is the rate that is in effect after the expiration of the teaser period.
CustomField.label: Interest Rate
